        the same.&nbsp; To that the little girl replies, �So when we have
        Cheerios, it�s like we�re having breakfast with Nana.�&nbsp; A tear then
        forms in Mom�s eye because grandma has obviously passed away.&nbsp;
        Leveraging the death of a grandparent to sell some cereal is an obvious
